<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Sobbi</title>
    <style>
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { .link-to-room { background-color:
      #f1e9dc !important; border: 3px solid #1c1c1c !important;} } @import
      url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300; background-color: #f2f2f2; } .container { width: 60%;
      background-color: white; } td { padding: 0; } table { border-spacing:
      16px; padding: 12px 10px; } .title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
      .web-site-name { text-decoration: none; } .logo-container { text-align:
      right; } .link { color: #1c1c1c; } .link_recommendation { font-weight:
      400; line-height: 24px; } .link_clarification { color: #979797; }
      .link-to-room { height: 60px; width: 240px; font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 13px; line-height: 58px; font-size: 25px; display:
      inline-block; text-decoration: none; background-color: #f1e9dc; border:
      3px solid #1c1c1c; user-select: none; transition: 0.2s; }
      .link-to-room_shadow { position: relative; } .link-to-room_front {
      transform: translate(-7px, -7px); position: absolute; display: block; }
      .link-to-room_front:active { transform: translate(-3px, -3px); }
      .simple-text { text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; } .clarification {
      color: #979797; font-size: 14px; } .button-container { text-align: center;
      height: 100px; } @media screen and (max-width: 600px) { .container {
      width: 80%; } } @media screen and (max-width: 400px) { .container { width:
      90%; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <br /><br />
    <center class='wrapper'>
      <table class='container'>
        <tr>
          <td class='logo-container'>
            <a
              class='title link web-site-name'
              href='https://sobbi.pw'
              target='_blank'
            >Sobbi</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='title'>ðŸ‘‹</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            Hi, I'm Alexander from the
            <a class='link' href='https://sobbi.pw' target='_blank'>Sobbi</a>
            interview platform and I have something to tell you.
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            You were invited to an interview as a spectator. This means that
            your company trusts you and asks for help in recruiting colleagues.
            Make a significant contribution to the building of the team. Help
            your interviewer partner during the interview with your advice,
            additional questions to ask, noticed nuances and aspects in his
            conversation with the interviewee. For this we have prepared a
            virtual room. Here are the details:
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            <strong>Date: </strong>{{date}}
            <br />
            <strong>Time: </strong>{{time}}
            (GMT)<br />
            <span class='clarification'>
              I can put it in your
              <a
                class='link_clarification'
                href='#'
                target='_blank'
              >Outlook</a>,
              <a class='link_clarification' href='#' target='_blank'>Google</a>
              or
              <a class='link_clarification' href='#' target='_blank'>iCal</a>
              calendar if you don't mind.
            </span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            <strong>Room name: </strong>{{roomName}}<br />
            <strong>Password: </strong>{{password}}<br />
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            <br />
            You don't have to remember it, but just press this button when the
            time comes.
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='button-container'>
            <a
              class='link-to-room link-to-room_shadow'
              target='_blank'
              href={{roomLink}}
            ><span class='title link link-to-room link-to-room_front'>Enter room</span></a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            Prepare a glass of water and try not to be late for it. At the
            bottom, I added a couple more articles with tips on how to pass the
            interview even better.
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  target='_blank'
                  class='link link_recommendation'
                >Clarifying questions - pill from lies.</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  target='_blank'
                  class='link link_recommendation'
                >Base of physiognomy in 20 minutes.</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href='#' target='_blank' class='link link_recommendation'>Did
                  you state that you developed software for the Apollo 11
                  program? Identify false projects.</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class='simple-text'>
            <strong>P.S. </strong>I believe in karma and your help will
            definitely come back to you ðŸ˜‰. Thank you and good luck.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </center>
    <br /><br />
  </body>
</html>